WARNING: DO NOT UPGRADE ARRAY AFTER DEPLOYMENT - fix is being worked out

Step 1: Download desired formation template
Step 2: Add desired tags to a yaml file. See example_tags.yaml for formatting guidance
Step 3: run the python script as such

python add_customer_tags.py -h
usage: add_customer_tags.py [-h] [--cft CFT] [--tags TAGS] [--output OUTPUT]

Add tags to a cloudformation template

optional arguments:
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --cft CFT        The path to the unedited cloudformation template
  --tags TAGS      The path to the yaml key value file containing the tags to
                   add
  --output OUTPUT  The path to the new modified template
